選擇下介入，進行執法行動」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>稱按機制可要求大學問責</strong><br />\n就大學校園被破壞，立法會議員梁美芬質疑教育局有否嘗試追究、監管大學，「我們賦予的大學自主，是否容許大學校園內不斷滋生的刑事行為？」楊潤雄回應，教育局有責任跟進大學工作，已要求學校就任何刑事毁壞事件報警。<span style=\"color: red;\">他稱大學撥款是由教育局、經大學教育資助委員會批出，按機制可要求大學就發生的事問責</span>，又說「（自己）未必日日高調走出來鬧、表達不滿」，但私下與大學管理層保持緊密的溝通，向他們說清楚要求。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191115/s00001/1573756168831/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191115%2Fs00001%2F1573756168831%2F&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjb9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=01073a77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191115%2Fs00001%2F1573756168831%2F&h=1d05821a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191115/s00001/1573756168831/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"問責局長呢？"},{"pid":"eb4c50bd8227c1c97eba5c7a2e195fbe9e80dabe","tid":1722666,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18ce0082d0f581f714ab25a1899b55c05b98e030","tid":1722666,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"校長：學校充份肯定本人工作，喺餘下任期將繼續為校園服務。"},{"pid":"0ecb30c4a526eb3505dbe03345dcb78302b8df50","tid":1722666,"uid":30782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"你條陷家產都未比人問責la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b6c2d1b06ffa43b5b156896b8083d4cc80d72a","tid":1722666,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:37:46.000Z","msg":"唔停課，導致學生翻學過程中受到不必要檢查同威嚇。佢第一個問責"},{"pid":"def21607f6b22c6b078284d0b58fd88204425e15","tid":1722666,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03: